features: 150 PIECE ROUND PUZZLE – Each beautifully illustrated boppi kid’s round puzzle is made up of 150 child-friendly jigsaw pieces.

100% RECYCLED EDUCATIONAL FUN – We love our planet, so our puzzles are eco-friendly and created using 100% recycled card. Educate through play by talking your child through the solar system, exploring the countries and people of the world, highlighting the changes of the seasons, or discovering the environments of animals around the world.

3-LAYERED JIGSAW PIECES – Each puzzle piece is created using a 3 layer extra thick cardboard with a fine linen-structured image layer and a firm and smooth backing layer, offering a tactile feel for little fingers.

58CM DIAMETER WITH ROUND GIFT BOX – When completed the boppi jigsaw puzzle has a diameter of 58cm and is accompanied with a pull-out image sheet. Each puzzle is presented in a colourfully illustrated round presentation gift box. Ideal for storing the puzzle pieces.

ILLUSTRATED BY LAURA WATSON – The boppi kid’s round jigsaw puzzles have been illustrated by Laura Watson. Laura is a Canadian based illustrator known for creating playful, cute, and endearing characters. Available puzzles in the range: Space, Dinosaurs, World Map, Seasons, Animals Around the World, and City Life.
